You haven't been to the cinema for a long time?

18
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:00,920
Not really.

19
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,720
Excuse me, excuse me.

20
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:13,560
Mr. Xia, I've got

21
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,400
another pack of popcorn as you requested.

22
