I was waiting for you at the airport for an hour.

25
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:08,680
Did you break up with Chu Nan?

26
00:04:09,480 --> 00:04:10,240
What would you like to eat?

27
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,360
This time I met

28
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,000
a French dessert chef in New York.

29
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,360
The mousse cakes he made

30
00:04:19,840 --> 00:04:21,240
can both amplify the sweetness of strawberries

31
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,800
and have the fragrant grassy taste from plants.

32
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,760
Do you know why?

33
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,440
Why the heck did you break up?

34
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:28,680
He added vervain,

35
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:31,160
the kind often used for aromatherapy.

36
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:40,360
Do you still love him?

37
00:04:43,760 --> 00:04:44,400
Xia Ke,

38
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:47,920
everyone in the world can ask me

39
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:48,920
why I broke up,

40
00:04:49,720 --> 00:04:50,960
but only you are not in a position to do so.

41
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,080
No matter why I broke up,

42
00:04:53,400 --> 00:04:55,160
as long as I find my happiness again,

43
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,480
you are still being held responsible.

44
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:03,360
Chu Nan's mother disliked me having married once

45
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,520
and having a child,

46
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:09,520
I have not wronged you
by putting the blame on you, have I?

47
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,280
Call me if there's anything I can do for you.

48
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,720
I'm sorry.

49
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:39,120
I've been busy with work recently
and I was really tired,

50
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,400
so I fell asleep accidentally halfway through.

51
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,160
It's OK, it's OK.

52
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:44,000
Had I known you were so tired,

53
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,400
