by asking you to keep me company.

54
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:46,520
It's not against my will at all.

55
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,280
Let's do it this way.

56
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:52,160
Let's watch a movie

57
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,200
you like next time.

58
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:55,920
Dating should make everybody happy.

59
00:05:57,080 --> 00:06:00,240
I like documentaries.

60
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:05,600
OK, OK. Let's watch a documentary next time.

61
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,800
