not shown in cinemas.

62
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:09,880
Where are they shown then?

63
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,280
At home.

64
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,560
Would you like to come over to watch it
at my place this weekend?

65
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,440
OK.

66
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:30,720
Have you made up your mind?

67
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:36,000
We are talking about watching a movie,

68
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:37,600
