69
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,880
Yes, it's watching a movie.

70
00:06:46,080 --> 00:06:47,080
But that said,

71
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,480
I haven't watched a documentary before.

72
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:49,720
I'm really looking forward to it.

73
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:52,960
I figure you like

74
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,920
human geography documentaries.

75
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:56,960
Geography was the subject I did worst in.

76
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,680
Was it? It happened to be my thing.

77
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,080
Really?

78
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:00,440
Yes.

79
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,640
You are awesome.

80
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:03,840
I always flunked the exams at school.

81
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,200
When it comes to geography,
you can also know a lot

82
