95
00:08:14,440 --> 00:08:15,160
Don't take it off.

96
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:16,080
Dance again for my dad

97
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:16,960
when he comes back later.

98
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,320
Don't take it off, don't take it off,
don't take it off.

99
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:19,600
To hell with dancing!

100
00:08:20,200 --> 00:08:22,240
My hipbones are almost broken.

101
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,720
Is it a special day again today?

102
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,120
