105
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:34,760
Falling-in-love anniversary, wedding anniversary

106
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:35,560
and moving house anniversary...

107
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:36,600
What is it for today?

108
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:40,240
Today is the anniversary of

109
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:43,000
our first  holiday in Spain.

110
00:08:44,880 --> 00:08:46,240
Daughter, I tell you what,

111
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:48,440
life should be informed by a sense of ritual

112
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,360
which makes a certain day

113
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:52,960
different from any other ordinary days

114
00:08:53,160 --> 00:08:54,520
and a certain moment

115
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,840
totally different
from any other ordinary moments.

116
00:09:00,120 --> 00:09:01,640
How's your date going with Chu Nan?

117
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:06,920
