120
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,360
Where are you, honey?

121
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:22,760
Where are you, honey?

122
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,040
Here I am, here I am!

123
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,080
Well, did you say yes?

124
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,240
I shouldn't have said yes, should I?

125
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,080
It seems things are

126
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,360
