131
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:01,440
Well, you are really thinking too much.

132
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,800
I specially confirmed with him yesterday.

133
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,400
We'll do nothing other than watch
a human geography documentary at his home.

134
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,760
Are you a single-celled creature?

135
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,240
Do you even believe that?

136
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,960
Even if you have no hands-on experience,

137
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,200
haven't you read girls' comics?

138
00:10:12,280 --> 00:10:12,680
Heck!

139
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:14,880
Just think it over with your walnut-sized brain.

140
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,400
Why does it cost so much for so little material?

141
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,440
Cabbage is cheap. Wear cabbages instead.

142
00:10:19,920 --> 00:10:21,280
This one is OK.

143
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,240
Forget it, forget it, forget it.

144
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:23,880
Try this on.

145
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:26,400
Forget it. How can I wear it?

146
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:27,320
This... this is too...

147
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:27,800
Go, go, go.

148
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,280
Well...

149
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:29,280
Do what an experienced hand says.

150
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:29,640
Why does this...

151
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,480
Try them on. I'm experienced.

152
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:33,920
Pick it up.

153
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:39,840
Mr. Xia.

154
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,400
Why are you here?

155
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,680
This is a question I should ask you, isn't it?

156
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,080
What's this?

157
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,480
It's nothing.

158
00:10:54,800 --> 00:10:58,480
I didn't expect you are a mascot like this.

159
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:02,080
Mr. Xia, as I've emphasized with you many times,

160
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,480
don't call me mascot anymore.

161
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:05,000
I'm a competent employee.

162
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,480
Not only can I draw,

163
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,320
I'll also submit

164
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,920
a satisfactory planning proposal this time.

165
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,640
Yes, Mr. Xia, you are thinking too much.

166
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:13,400
This is not routine shopping.

167
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:15,320
It's a special circumstance today.

168
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,040
She has a date.

169
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:20,880
Are you going to his home?

170
00:11:22,560 --> 00:11:24,960
Well, I'm just going there to watch a documentary.

171
00:11:27,280 --> 00:11:29,120
Xia Ke, come over to pay the bill for me.

172
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,040
I tell you what,

173
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:32,040
wait here for me!

174
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:41,920
Is the pin number the same as before?

175
00:11:44,920 --> 00:11:45,520
Hello, Miss.

176
00:11:45,520 --> 00:11:46,800
You've reached the consumption threshold of 2,000 yuan

177
00:11:46,800 --> 00:11:48,080
to get a pair of silk stockings for free.

178
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:49,240
Which pair would you like?

179
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:53,360
Which one do you think is better?

180
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,440
Anything is fine.

181
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,240
Touch them with your hand.

182
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,680
These pairs are different.

183
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,200
What are you doing? Hurry up.

184
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,600
Choose a color for me.

185
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:12,680
