186
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:15,640
Men are the best consultants for such matters.

187
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,000
I'll have this pair.

188
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,400
Let me get a new pair for you.

189
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:26,800
What are you looking at?

190
00:12:29,160 --> 00:12:30,000
Chu Nan's new girlfriend.

191
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:41,240
Why are we running?

192
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:42,760
Are you a fool?

193
00:12:43,760 --> 00:12:44,400
Didn't you see

194
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,080
