195
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:50,640
Gee whiz, Mr. Xia has always claimed himself to be single.

196
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,680
I thought he liked you.

197
00:12:54,680 --> 00:12:57,160
Xu Yiyi, you have very outlandish imagination.

198
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:58,960
No, I'm serious.

199
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:01,840
Originally I thought he just liked to make fun of you,

200
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,680
but ever since your blind date worked out,

201
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:05,120
he has become very out of the ordinary.

202
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,080
You see, just now

203
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:08,040
when he heard you are going
to Chu Nan's home in the evening,

204
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:10,200
his face turned green at once.

205
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,400
He's not that kind of person.

206
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:15,280
Don't rush to deny it first.

207
00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:16,680
Give it a second thought.

208
00:13:17,280 --> 00:13:19,680
Do you like the domineering CEO or not?

209
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,580
(Salary: 4,813)

210
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,280
(Salary: 7,071)

211
00:13:32,780 --> 00:13:33,580
(Salary: 10,898)

212
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:37,480
(Salary: 15,615)

213
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:49,320
Of course I like him.

214
00:13:49,520 --> 00:13:51,160
I've had four pay rises in two years.

215
00:13:51,440 --> 00:13:53,360
He's my hard-won special express train

216
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:54,560
taking me to my ambitions.

217
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:55,720
I'll hold onto him tightly.

218
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,320
You walnut head!

219
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,120
It's not even as big as a thin-shelled walnut,

220
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,360
probably only as big as a pecan.

221
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,760
You'll get the hang of it when pigs fly.

222
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:07,200
I'm content enough to maintain a longstanding and pure

223
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,400
monetary relationship with Mr. Xia.

224
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,360
What's more, I already have Chu Nan.

225
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,160
Wait and see.

226
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:14,080
I'm sure Mr. Xia will

227
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:16,480
do whatever he can to stop you tonight.

228
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,600
Didn't you say before we came here

229
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:22,240
that you are gonna usher
in tonight's victory for me?

230
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:25,760
Yes, yes, yes, victory.

231
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:26,920
We can't let that Mr. Xia who thinks

232
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:28,360
the grass is always greener
on the other side of the fence have his way!

233
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,720
We must win victory to piss him off!

234
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:34,240
Let's go to another battlefield bra shop.

235
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:34,880
Let's go.

236
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,360
Well, are you not done with it yet?

237
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:43,400
You've also brought your laptop.

238
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,160
Yes. I'm afraid I'll be asked to do something
on short notice by my company.

239
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:48,360
I really envy your boss

240
00:14:48,400 --> 00:14:49,560
for having an employee like you

241
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:50,640
who's on call 24 hours a day.

242
00:14:51,680 --> 00:14:52,440
Here, let me carry it for you.

243
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,120
Thanks.

244
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:53,800
It's OK.

245
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:00,520
Is... is someone in?

246
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:06,000
Xing Yun, you are here.

247
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,080
Be quick to come in. Be quick to come in.

248
00:15:08,920 --> 00:15:09,320
This is my mother.

249
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,040
Here, here, here. Be quick to come in.

250
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:11,280
Hello, aunt.

251
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:12,040
Hello.

252
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,520
Well, I... I... I...

253
00:15:14,680 --> 00:15:16,120
No need to change your shoes.
No need to change your shoes.

254
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:17,120
Come in. It's OK.

255
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:17,680
No need.

256
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,320
Xing Yun is here.

257
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:23,560
Hello, I'm Chu Nan's father.

258
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:24,560
Hello, uncle.

259
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:25,440
Hello, hello.

260
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:29,680
Here you are.

261
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:30,640
Thanks, aunt.

262
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:35,560
Rest assured,

263
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:37,960
I've got a house ready for your marriage.

264
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:40,200
It's in a good location with convenient transportation.

265
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:44,480
Mom, this is not what Xing Yun meant.

266
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:45,520
I know.

267
00:15:46,160 --> 00:15:47,720
I said it just to make the girl feel reassured.

268
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:50,600
Young people nowadays all like living
with their other half on their own,

269
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:51,600
right?

270
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:53,880
What kind of decoration do you like?

271
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:56,360
